<br>
1. Yes you do Deserve Phat Lewt/Praise For all the time That you have put up being Playing This game.. i know many of you have been playing this game that it has come out and ive only been playing 8 months And I salute all of You that have earned what you deserve <br>
<br>
2. I realize That A schedule/GM &quot;Coordinator&quot; type of thing wont work since The Abundance Of players is too much To handle even if you assign one GM per player (impossible also). Also sadly but true..people Crave Power/&quot;territory&quot; Since thats how society has made us, I do not Believe That People Make society Bad just , Its just the way the world goes (Example: The Renaissance, Dark Ages) People Were so happy with each other and enjoyed life during the renaissance, But Struggled To Survive Plagues and did anything Possible in their power to overpower others. Well Anyways I think history repeats itself and something good will come =P.<br>
<br>
3.Monopoly. Word That we hear in RL and Many Companies are being accused of Being ( microsoft, At&amp;T, etc..). They Earned It, They came First, They were the originals, <br>
SOLUTION=dont Fight it Just be original and create/make something different that will appeal people (Throwing some theology In here so if i offend anyone sorry =( ) God Created Us to Achieve Prosper, Live happily with one another and share, Invent, Create, Make the World A better Place.... So just Fulfill your duty as a human and do those things above IMO, We are all going to die someday and we have a beautiful Life After Death, So why not leave Something nice for our children to live in when we go ?<br>
<br>
4. In conclusion..sorry For Making such a big deal out of things..i think i went Off track on what i was really supposed to say =P. Just be happy, Continue Life, Do everything in your Power to make it great, you only live once, Its a Game but with much Human Aspects and Emotion in it.. thats why we are all so hooked into this game , Its life but in another world.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Im Egrothius and thes are my 2 (4 if you will =P) Cents<br>
<br>
